name: PROPERTIES 05 - Supermarket in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood.
The small supermarket is located in the central area of ​​Little Nostalgia, despite its small dimensions, it maintains a great variety and quantity of products that you cannot imagine! You have to be careful with the drawers, since being so small they overflow with merchandise and sometimes it can fall on you!
It maintains a parking area for its clients and is open 24 hours a day.
Land measurements: 60m x 90m
